*Movement and Flow Types are Live!*






Managing modern logistics requires more than just moving packages; it
requires a system that understands the unique "DNA" of every single order.
*We are handing you the controls by bringing Token-Level Management* to the
forefront of your dashboard.


This update isn't just about labeling a direction; it=E2=80=99s about build=
ing a
smarter, more descriptive framework for your entire operation. By allowing
you to define specific movement and flow types now.


What=E2=80=99s New?



Once you=E2=80=99ve picked your allocation method, you can now fine-tune ev=
ery
token with *Dynamic Movement Controls*

   -

   *Movement Type (The Journey):* A clean, single-select dropdown to toggle
   between *Forward* or *Reverse* logistics.
   -

   *Flow Type (The Operational Complexity):* Need to handle a specific
   operational aspect? This multi-select menu lets you layer complex flows =
on
   top of your journey:



*The Flow Models*


Customize your operation with one-click logic layers based on movement type=
:

   -

   *QR FIFO:* *Blind Dispatching.* Riders receive zero order info until
   they physically scan the QR code on-site.
   -

   *Update FIFO:* *Synchronized Pickups.* Orders are pre-allocated, but
   "Pickup" is enabled only when the merchant pushes a real-time order upda=
te.
   -

   *Partial:* *Ultimate Flexibility.* Stop the "all-or-nothing" bottleneck.
   Pick up or deliver only what the customer wants.



*Running a standard route? No selection required for your everyday flows.*
[image: Frame.png]


Why It=E2=80=99s Good for you!

   -

   *Total Versatility:* From simple doorstep drops to complex QR-coded
   reverse logistics, you now have a single dashboard that does it all.
   -

   *Instant Execution:* Scale your operations without getting lost in the
   settings.

Thats It!


Stay tuned for more updates.
